				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Erudites, I think, are the best race to be. I'm a level 9 Enchanter and I have 120 intellegence. The best thing about being an Enchanter is the fact that we can turn invisible and cross zone without fear. And when we need to go to places that hate us, we can just turn into whatever the race is there. And when we're passing through zones and the illusion fades, we can just turn invisible before we go in. Another good thing about being an Enchanter is the fact that if we do all of what I just said, we can go to Neriak, get the spell &quot;Enchant Silver,&quot; make silver and get paid at the same time(being a Dark Elf of course!)! And if we get attacked by something that is a higher level than us, we can easily cast fear on it and make it run away(the spell doesn't work on madmen simply because they're insane and should have no reason to fear anything!) and then cast &quot;Memory Blur&quot; on it so it won't come back! So in conclusion, we really are the High Men...and Women<BR>
